{{champion:39}} is one I want to become a star guardian badly.

{{champion:51}} {{champion:22}} {{champion:131}} {{champion:89}} {{champion:84}} {{champion:43}}  {{champion:163}} 

Could be good candidates too.

I can believe some of these. Taliyah is a popular fan pick for the skin line, and I can just visualize Caitlyn and Sejuani. Evelynn has potential, but she doesn't seem like the type who would defend the universe. I mostly doubt Zoe though, since Riot showed what looked like a pool party skin for her that will probably be here this year, and I doubt they'd put two skins on Zoe when they have yet to make another one for my boy Kled...
Really Riot just make me a Kled skin...
